{"tid":532313,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以講野細聲啲","createTime":"2018-01-17T16:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T20:09:12.000Z","uid":151781,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"070dfb3ed142c9be02febe1d417fd7bdcd81ae97","tid":532313,"uid":151781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:56:14.000Z","msg":"我天生就係個好易high既人，一high就會好大聲講野，尤其笑果陣，我真係試過係旺角笑然後周圍啲人望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實我真係果刻真係意識唔到自己講野大聲，係返到屋企諗返起或者朋友話我知我先意識到<br />\n而我又唔係唔可以細聲講野，好多人岩岩識我果陣都話我講野好斯文好細聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道自己好矛盾，但我真心想向各位求救<br />\n究竟點先可以係興奮既時候講野唔好咁大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a5f57fb95da30399819630ad227106768846f1","tid":532313,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"割左個喉嚨佢"},{"pid":"beeb7a547e127329c60fd82852969a7a2c4dca2e","tid":532313,"uid":769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:59:16.000Z","msg":"唔好咁興奮"},{"pid":"f04b91076d1d10a20adf466ec2a22b65b33978ed","tid":532313,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T16:59:48.000Z","msg":"我呀媽都係咁 嘈撚到仆街"},{"pid":"936526a2cc1d9e197406c268c4ab4cd892f4ba31","tid":532313,"uid":28972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"唔好睇咁多金在奐 就可能靜啲"},{"pid":"1649d28acc6088d02fc25d35a456287b168ee2ce","tid":532313,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T17:39:39.000Z","msg":"俾耳機佢"},{"pid":"186aaf7540d4ec2c171374b312332d1490c7fd00","tid":532313,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T20:35:25.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d3c4211b033a0bb1e3811335f290a202f75fc5","tid":532313,"uid":15177